{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069220/extras/header.png?t=1613230254\" /><br>Miniturn is a turn-based 1v1 <strong>multiplayer</strong> strategy game.<br>It can be played competitively or just for fun on a casual basis.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069220/extras/game-play_header.png?t=1613230254\" /><br>It is a <strong>card game</strong> that has its own twist. Your health is your money.<br>You play on a small 16x16 grid map and after you played a card in the game<br>you have control over the unit and you can direct their fate or lead them into battle.<br><br>A match of Miniturn is usually won by one side when the enemy's Crystal has been<br>destroyed.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069220/extras/contact_header.png?t=1613230254\" /><br>Due to a small player base, we can't guarantee that there is another player in the queue at<br>all times, so we recommend joining our official <strong>MiniTurn Discord server</strong> to find someone<br>to play with. (You can find a <strong>discord invite</strong> on our website and in-game)<br><br>Good luck and have fun playing,<br>Max Coppen and Christopher Freund","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069220/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1613230254","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069220/page.bg.jpg?t=1613230254","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069220/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1613230254","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069220/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1613230254","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Steam Achievements",